        <note appliesTo="source">line: 8</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="initial">
        <source>This add-on, partly based on Tony's Enhancements by Tony Malykh, adds the ability to split audio from NVDA and other sounds onto separate audio channels.</source>
        <target>This add-on, partly based on Tony's Enhancements by Tony Malykh, adds the ability to split audio from NVDA and other sounds onto separate audio channels.</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
